English.Text: Silver cutlery embossed with the names Hades and Styx. These are from Sir John's expedition ships! There are also cufflinks belonging to Sir John engraved with assorted marsupials, and a knife handle with the emblem of the Arctic council. Tapeesa says that about a year ago, some men came wanting to know about channels through the ice, and traded their things for information. She points to the west coast of Labrador Island on your map.
